---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Data Complaints" description="How to raise a data-protection complaint with VisualWalkthroughs.">
  <div class="legal-wrap">
    <h1>Data-Protection Complaints</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <p>If you're unhappy with how we've handled your personal data, here's how to raise a complaint.</p>

    <h2>Step 1 — contact us</h2>
    <p>Email <a href="mailto:eevee.bork@icloud.com">eevee.bork@icloud.com</a> with "Data complaint" in the subject line. Please describe what happened and what outcome you're looking for.</p>

    <h2>What happens next</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>We will acknowledge your complaint within 5 working days.</li>
      <li>We will investigate and respond with an outcome within 30 days.</li>
      <li>We keep a log of complaints and how they were resolved.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Step 2 — escalate to the ICO</h2>
    <p>If you're still unhappy after our response, you can complain to the Information Commissioner's Office at <a href="https://ico.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ico.org.uk</a>.</p>
  </div>
</Base>
